{"tid":1407243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[制裁紅媒] 禁止 CCTVB 採訪","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:16:30.000Z","uid":274607,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"188db96e180f40a90564caa138b6ac41774827ef","tid":1407243,"uid":274607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打成功推到 foodpanda 唔再係 CCTVB 落廣告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n接下黎，除左繼續向係 CCTVB 落廣告既公司施壓<br />\n仲要向係 CCTVB 做新聞部既人施壓<br />\n<br />\n不過我地都明，有 d 人可能真係要養家，好難一下子唔撈 <br />\n所以，我地可以<span style=\"color: red;\">阻住 CCTVB 採訪 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如今日就有巴打叫停架車然後將車身噴白 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n架車比人阻住左，記者採訪唔到，上頭都唔可以講咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果佢地連 CCTVB 採訪車都唔出<br />\n就一齊再諗<br />\n<br />\n<strong>記協話咩妨礙新聞自由都唔撚理<br />\n除非記協你有方法令 CCTVB 唔再亂報新聞呃 9 香港人 </strong>"},{"pid":"acb3282dc548738e4fc6be70fb92352a1ff187c9","tid":1407243,"uid":231443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:04:10.000Z","msg":"已經裝左佢個直播app，預備聽日捉cctvb派出既鬼"},{"pid":"c5a3c05bc048dddf13ad3adf70a5dd60ae5a9275","tid":1407243,"uid":274607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834e451eeea5e2f868c2cecd7c39b358785a8b71","tid":1407243,"uid":274607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:08:15.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"ad9d826f529010090b79cb9d6f061a41b7bc78b0","tid":1